ygData.messageBody:
Just wait till Wednesday, after the patch. This will be one of the
"experience bonus" zones. After the patch goes live, get a full group of 6
people and head to sol A. You'll then get a double max bonus.

After you go, try to report back here to this news group and let us know how
much of a bonus you noticed in your experience.

Micromu
52 Vicar
Sistily
47 Warrior
